# ================================================================
# Railway 部署配置
# 使用 Railway 的 Nixpacks 自动检测构建
# Push 到 GitHub 后，在 Railway 面板连接仓库即可自动部署
# ================================================================

[build]
  builder = "nixpacks"
  buildCommand = "cd frontend && npm ci && npm run build && cd .. && mvn clean package -DskipTests"

[deploy]
  numReplicas = 1
  startCommand = "java -jar target/webchat-server-*.jar"
  healthcheckPath = "/actuator/health"
  healthcheckTimeout = 60

# 环境变量在 Railway Dashboard 中设置:
# RAILWAY_ENVIRONMENT=production
# MYSQL_HOST=     ← 使用 Railway MySQL 插件
# MYSQL_PORT=3306
# MYSQL_USER=root
# MYSQL_PASSWORD= ← Railway 自动提供
# MYSQL_DATABASE=webchat
# MONGO_HOST=     ← 使用 Railway MongoDB 插件
# MONGO_PORT=27017
# REDIS_HOST=     ← 使用 Railway Redis 插件
# REDIS_PORT=6379
# JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret

# 前置依赖（在 Railway Dashboard 中添加）:
# 1. MySQL 插件
# 2. MongoDB 插件
# 3. Redis 插件
